Program: Outlook
Title: Athletes Doping in the GDR
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrvw
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Katharina Bullin and the other former East German athletes who are suing for compensation for being given performance enhancing drugs without their knowledge in the 1980s. Also, analysing listeners dreams; South african street kids, Twilight Children and the film Tsotsi.